{"tid":745022,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得未試過中學時期拍拖覺得好後悔？","createTime":"2018-07-16T11:41:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T15:41:37.000Z","uid":71508,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a55ad1ff419263db26c4a6a49973d2e868eccbac","tid":745022,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T11:41:30.000Z","msg":"我覺得我中學果陣冇拍過拖，好似冇青春過，浪費光陰，未試過同學生妹係海邊傾心事，甚至未試過一齊5點睇日落吹下海邊風，其實學生時期既戀愛係最純潔，比較上冇咁現實冇咁物質主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n未試過係中學時期同女仔一齊hea真係好後悔，我中學好似完全白過咁，諗返起以前我放學就即刻返屋企，都唔知做乜春？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：非羅定偉主義，只係好後悔未試過中學時期拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 覺得人生好似有一個空白左！青春啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d3ac275bb12071f93bfd005bb6038aea098e82","tid":745022,"uid":21355,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T11:43:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59ced9ea29aa883abe937f362b03d4419906446","tid":745022,"uid":194525,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T11:45:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/16/194506_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F16%2F194506_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=423077a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樓主又嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces